Output assets/demo-diff.gif

Set Shell zsh
Set FontSize 13
Set Width 1200
Set Height 750
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 16
Set TypingSpeed 25ms
Set CursorBlink false

Hide
Type "cd /Users/hadi.farhat/Documents/Explore/promptdiff && clear"
Enter
Sleep 0.5s
Show

Type "promptdiff diff tests/fixtures/prompts/support-agent-v3.prompt tests/fixtures/prompts/support-agent-v7.prompt --annotate --context 1"
Enter
Sleep 5s
